kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nUO1013 ETA HKG: 1515，但UO1646原本ETD from HKG係1305"},{"pid":"f0a9f0863d82886dd21ec1c8db1fbb077cc4d0ec","tid":444493,"uid":59602,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乘的士到酒店已花24,000日圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿教授嘅應變能力真高，有九個字skyliner出返市區唔揀，居然搭的士"},{"pid":"f68925027cd617434638cc8f57032a3e70754203","tid":444493,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:34:08.000Z","msg":"見到貪平啲人要負出代價係特別爽"},{"pid":"42182c877fea1b3792b2180262e27c70503e9101","tid":444493,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乘的士到酒店已花24,000日圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿教授嘅應變能力真高，有九個字skyliner出返市區唔揀，居然搭的士</blockquote><br />\n凌晨一點先有行李嘔返出o黎呀，班機delay原因係NRT唔係24小時運作呀"},{"pid":"7655cbd11c93e0715dbbfd56d0fb7843a7070eeb","tid":444493,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"每次一有延誤一定係話冇衫著冇藥食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec11384231046da4b2489e4b7e501cee589d3c0","tid":444493,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"UO飛NRT試過唔入油就趕2300士前飛走，最後班機要先去KIX入油先再返到香港，我都幾好奇當時隻機land KIX夠唔夠30 mins reserve fuel<img src=\"/assets/fac