026086d33e3","tid":444493,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>畢完業第一份工坐CX定港龍又係成田飛差唔多時間，4300$ 一張<br />\n一樣Delay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 印象好深</blockquote><br />\n但係因航一定會做好多野去盡量縮短delay時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜都無，坐係登機口度呆等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩臨close前飛到"},{"pid":"e41541231ead0620f79e22ab023b9cf182a02f91","tid":444493,"uid":122997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乘的士到酒店已花24,000日圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿教授嘅應變能力真高，有九個字skyliner出返市區唔揀，居然搭的士</blockquote><br />\n凌晨一點先有行李嘔返出o黎呀，班機delay原因係NRT唔係24小時運作呀</blockquote><br />\n成田機場個件終極釘子戶幾時死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜事,有冇詳情?"},{"pid":"535a3c94cb7691d4459d2a8f82a20abf81bd4833","tid":444493,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一有特價咪又成班乞兒去搶,<br />\n呢間野存在價值, 只係HOLD住個低價位就夠。<br />\n坐? 不了, 反正咁大機會要俾貴錢, 點解我唔一開始就揀貴機?<br />\n一年去得個一次, 貪DELAY, CANCEL好玩啊?</blockquote><br />\n最慘係呢條航線delay history 其他公司都見紅<br />\n搞到唔知坐咩好"},{"pid":"68eedd830ab957e83fb7b299e106365dea00485c","tid":444493,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>UO飛NRT試過唔入油就趕2300士前飛走，最後班機要先去KIX入油先再返到香港，我都幾好奇當時隻機land KIX夠唔夠30 mins reserve fuel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大鑊都冇report?<br />\n佢用咩原因同KIX講要降落？</blockquote><br />\n駛鬼report咩，crew無declare low fuel就當無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛去中途port入油其實無乜問題，前題係隻機真係有reserve fuel，大柴飛長途有時都因為天氣或者運作原因中途要加油既，但連咁短程都要咁玩就真係UO先玩得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時好似巴士咁有得撳掣有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b23ca708ff5ff9fb8601c6de993babc2b7c7b4","tid":444493,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲話做商學院教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSPACE渣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fbe.hku.hk/staff/academic/detail/baniel-cheung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbe.hku.hk%2Fstaff%2Facademic%2Fdetail%2Fbaniel-cheung&d=ytPBNWVX11MqgvXu93vcRWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=be5f180a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fbe.hku.hk/staff/academic/detail/baniel-cheung</a><